There will be three features:

--enable-vrtc-host
	Enable the VRT Control host code.
	Requires: GNU Radio libgruel and BSD sockets
	Creates: libvrtchost.{so,a}

--enable-vrtc-device
	Enable the VRT Control device code.
	Requires: nothing
	Creates: libvrtcdevice.{so,a}

--enable-vrtc-device-sim
	Enable the host-based device simulator.
	Requires: vrtc-device and BSD sockets
	Creates: device simulator executable


FIXME For now, they are all enabled.
